  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    This class defines specific account by using setter and getter methods

    Stores account types in database, searches for account in database, add account to database, removes account from database, print by last name and by date

    Stores information of checking account opened by a specific holder
    Date
    Stores date of which the specified account was opened
    MoneyMarket
    Stores information of money market account opened by a specific holder
    Profile
    Stores information of account holder
    RunProject2
    This class runs the TransactionManager().java program
    Savings
    Stores information of savings account opened by a specific holder
    TransactionManager
    This class handles all user inputs as well as error checking and data type mismatches
